<% content_for :title, "Politique de Confidentialite — Vera Trade" %>

<section class="relative bg-bg-primary min-h-screen">
  <div class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto px-5 lg:px-10 py-20 lg:py-32">

    <p class="eyebrow text-accent-red mb-6">Protection des donnees</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-[40px] lg:text-[56px] leading-[1.05] text-text-primary mb-4">
      Politique de
      <br /><span class="playfair-italic">Confidentialite</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-text-muted mb-16">
      Conformement au RGPD (UE) 2016/679 — Derniere mise a jour : [A COMPLETER]
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-14 font-body text-[15px] text-text-secondary leading-[1.8]">

      <%# --- 1 --- %>
      <article>
        <h2 class="label-small text-accent-red mb-4">1. Responsable du traitement</h2>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p><span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Identite :</span> Vera Trade [A COMPLETER : forme juridique]</p>
          <p><span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Siege social :</span> [A COMPLETER], Lyon, France</p>
          <p><span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Email DPO :</span> <span class="font-mono">bonjour@veratrade.fr</span></p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <%# --- 2 --- %>
      <article>
        <h2 class="label-small text-accent-red mb-4">2. Donnees collectees</h2>
        <p>Dans le cadre de votre utilisation de la Plateforme, nous collectons les donnees suivantes :</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 pl-5">
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Donnees d'identification :</span> prenom, nom, adresse email, telephone
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Donnees de connexion :</span> adresse IP, type de navigateur, horodatage
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Donnees vehicules :</span> informations relatives aux annonces publiees
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Donnees de transaction :</span> historique des encheres, messages echanges
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Documents KYC :</span> piece d'identite (si verification demandee)
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <%# --- 3 --- %>
      <article>
        <h2 class="label-small text-accent-red mb-4">3. Finalites du traitement</h2>
        <p>Vos donnees sont traitees pour les finalites suivantes :</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 pl-5">
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            Gestion de votre compte utilisateur et authentification
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            Publication et gestion de vos annonces de vehicules
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            Facilitation des encheres et mise en relation acheteur-vendeur
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            Verification d'identite (KYC) pour la securite des transactions
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            Communication de service (notifications, alertes)
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            Amelioration de la Plateforme et analyse statistique anonymisee
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <%# --- 4 --- %>
      <article>
        <h2 class="label-small text-accent-red mb-4">4. Bases legales</h2>
        <p>Les traitements de donnees reposent sur les bases legales suivantes :</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 pl-5">
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Execution du contrat :</span> creation de compte, publication d'annonces, encheres
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Consentement :</span> cookies non essentiels, communications marketing
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Interet legitime :</span> securite de la Plateforme, prevention de la fraude
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Obligation legale :</span> conservation des donnees de transaction
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <%# --- 5 --- %>
      <article>
        <h2 class="label-small text-accent-red mb-4">5. Duree de conservation</h2>
        <div class="border border-line rounded-sm overflow-hidden">
          <table class="w-full">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-line">
                <th class="label-small text-left px-5 py-3">Categorie</th>
                <th class="label-small text-left px-5 py-3">Duree</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="font-body text-[14px]">
              <tr class="border-b border-line/50">
                <td class="px-5 py-3 text-text-primary">Donnees de compte</td>
                <td class="px-5 py-3">Duree du compte + 3 ans</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-line/50">
                <td class="px-5 py-3 text-text-primary">Donnees de transaction</td>
                <td class="px-5 py-3">10 ans (obligation legale)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-line/50">
                <td class="px-5 py-3 text-text-primary">Documents KYC</td>
                <td class="px-5 py-3">5 ans apres la derniere verification</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="px-5 py-3 text-text-primary">Logs de connexion</td>
                <td class="px-5 py-3">1 an</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </article>

      <%# --- 6 --- %>
      <article>
        <h2 class="label-small text-accent-red mb-4">6. Destinataires des donnees</h2>
        <p>Vos donnees peuvent etre communiquees aux destinataires suivants :</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 pl-5">
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Sous-traitants techniques :</span> hebergeur (Vercel), base de donnees (Supabase, EU), envoi d'emails ([A COMPLETER])
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Autres utilisateurs :</span> informations publiques de votre profil vendeur
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Autorites competentes :</span> sur requisition judiciaire uniquement
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Aucune donnee n'est vendue a des tiers. Les transferts hors UE sont encadres par
          des clauses contractuelles types (CCT) conformement au RGPD.
        </p>
      </article>

      <%# --- 7 --- %>
      <article>
        <h2 class="label-small text-accent-red mb-4">7. Vos droits</h2>
        <p>Conformement au RGPD, vous disposez des droits suivants :</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 pl-5">
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Droit d'acces :</span> obtenir une copie de vos donnees personnelles
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Droit de rectification :</span> corriger des donnees inexactes ou incompletes
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Droit a l'effacement :</span> demander la suppression de vos donnees
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Droit a la portabilite :</span> recevoir vos donnees dans un format structure
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Droit d'opposition :</span> vous opposer au traitement pour motif legitime
          </li>
          <li class="relative before:content-['—'] before:absolute before:-left-5 before:text-accent-red">
            <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Droit a la limitation :</span> limiter temporairement le traitement
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-6">
          Pour exercer vos droits, ecrivez a :
          <span class="font-mono text-text-primary">bonjour@veratrade.fr</span>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Vous pouvez egalement introduire une reclamation aupres de la CNIL :
          <span class="font-mono text-text-primary">cnil.fr</span>
        </p>
      </article>

      <%# --- 8 --- %>
      <article>
        <h2 class="label-small text-accent-red mb-4">8. Securite</h2>
        <p>
          Vera Trade met en oeuvre des mesures techniques et organisationnelles appropriees
          pour proteger vos donnees contre tout acces non autorise, perte, alteration ou
          divulgation. Les connexions sont chiffrees via HTTPS, les mots de passe sont haches
          avec bcrypt, et les donnees sont hebergees dans des centres certifies en Union Europeenne.
        </p>
      </article>

      <%# --- 9 --- %>
      <article>
        <h2 class="label-small text-accent-red mb-4">9. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          La Plateforme utilise exclusivement des cookies strictement necessaires au
          fonctionnement du service (session utilisateur, jeton CSRF). Aucun cookie
          publicitaire ou de tracage tiers n'est depose.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          [A COMPLETER : si mise en place d'analytics, decrire les cookies, leur finalite
          et le mecanisme de consentement]
        </p>
      </article>

      <%# --- 10 --- %>
      <article>
        <h2 class="label-small text-accent-red mb-4">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Pour toute question relative a la protection de vos donnees personnelles :
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Email :</span>
          <span class="font-mono text-text-primary">bonjour@veratrade.fr</span>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          <span class="text-text-primary font-medium">Adresse :</span>
          Vera Trade — [A COMPLETER], Lyon, France
        </p>
      </article>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
